1
00:00:11,430 --> 00:00:13,930
Oh no, I overslept!

2
00:00:13,930 --> 00:00:15,970
Why didn't you wake me up?

3
00:00:15,970 --> 00:00:18,060
I did try to wake you!

4
00:00:18,060 --> 00:00:21,860
Besides, I'm not your mother.

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,690
No time!
Save the lecture for later!

6
00:00:29,150 --> 00:00:32,570
Oh!

7
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:47,170
Hinata!

8
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,730
Huh? Mizuki?

9
00:01:01,190 --> 00:01:04,310
What are you doing here?

10
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,940
You forgot your lunch.

11
00:01:06,940 --> 00:01:11,150
Oh, wow! You're right. Thanks!

12
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:13,570
I can't believe you brought it all this way.

13
00:01:13,570 --> 00:01:15,580
I really appreciate it.

14
00:01:17,490 --> 00:01:19,450
Oh, Kamiki-san!

15
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:21,000
He's a senior colleague I can always count on.

16
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,880
I've mentioned him before.

17
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:30,050
Thank you for taking care of Hinata.
I'm his older brother, Mizuki.

18
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:31,710
Oh.

19
00:01:31,750 --> 00:01:33,510
Hinata talks about you all the time.

20
00:01:33,510 --> 00:01:34,720
His amazing older brother.

21
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:38,470
It's nice to meet you.
